Link for the recipe is up in the bio now! ⁣
⁣
Few things are more refreshing than a fresh wrapped summer roll. The textures are a blend of soft and sticky from the wrapper, mixed with the crunch of fresh vegetables. These are perfect for spring, summer, and any time you want a quick lunch. ⁣
⁣
I also love to make these ahead of time since they keep in the fridge pretty well. ⁣
⁣
This peanut sauce by the way, SO good! You can use this peanut sauce for so many things beyond this recipe. I even contemplated making it it's own stand alone recipe. Maybe I'll do that later so it's easier to find, but YES! These spring rolls wouldn't be complete with out it. 🥜⁣
⁣
Hope you're having a great Friday and have some super fun plans for the weekend. See you on Monday! ⁣
